title: Beaver Builder Pro 2.1.5.1 - WordPress Page Builder
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Beaver Builder WordPress Plugin is the page builder you can trust with your business. Take control and join over 500,000 WordPress websites built with Beaver Builder. Beaver Builder 2.1.5.1 is a complete design system that includes a page builder plugin and a framework theme. Positioning text and images with the WordPress editor is a pain! Beaver Builder’s front end drag and drop interface gives you total control over the layout of your pages. Nulled Beaver Builder WordPress Plugin can be used with any theme and you can switch themes without losing your content. Even if you decide to stop using Beaver Builder, your content gets ported right back into the WordPress editor. Beaver Builder Pro WordPress Plugin Features Separate your page builder from your theme and get complete control of your content. Join over 100,000 websites using the flexible and powerful Beaver Builder Theme. You can position images and text with precision, and build column based layouts in minutes. Kick-start your creativity with dozens of gorgeous page templates
